item.title: About
item.description: Welcome to my site, stranger! Happy to have you here. My first “home page” went online shortly after I got access to the Internet, which was approximately in 1997. I’ve maintained my site through high school first using Microsoft Frontpage, then later I taught myself HTML and CSS to design my web page. Back in the day, everybody had their personal space, for example, with a link section to other interesting sites.
